{"tid":2241213,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"香港/喺外國/回流香港 呢個谷都等緊你入嚟","createTime":"2020-10-13T07:12:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-22T12:03:54.000Z","uid":9178,"like":10,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"db319aabd66172717b023d66f790f06b0079b22e","tid":2241213,"uid":9178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T07:12:45.000Z","msg":"香港人/喺外國嘅香港人/回流香港嘅<br />\n呢個谷都歎迎你 交友無分界限<br />\n<span class=\"red\">唔想出聚？冇問題！正係出聲都得</span><br />\n但入嚟潛水就唔好啦 <br />\n暫時谷中24小時都有人 因為唔同國家嘅人都有（並唔係指定某地方）<br />\n外國巴絲唔洗擔心時間唔啱 係外國嘅你地可以自行搞聚<br />\n<span class=\"red\">呢到啲外國巴絲已經成功搞過聚啦</span><br />\n係香港/返嚟冇耐嘅你 識下朋友 吹下水 <br />\n有意就填form<br />\nset咗只可填一次 所以要登入 唔想人重複又重複咁填<br />\n擔心嘅就唔好入 個人選擇 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/gC7kbacAVX7pEggE8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FgC7kbacAVX7pEggE8&d=uoj2XAvVwhv3g67ADWIJbZR%2B4kUINcy65scadR%2F1ewI%3D&h=b92633e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/gC7kbacAVX7pEggE8</a>"},{"pid":"4d4fb54070a33d3311c40d4061b894c9d114dbf6","tid":2241213,"uid":9178,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T09:48:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87e62eac8f845a34873697d06d9f03c1ddd13634","tid":2241213,"uid":75692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T09:48:45.000Z","msg":"what group?<br />\ntg?"},{"pid":"43ae0d76d18a99e9e8164a32e779e26f85abc917","tid":2241213,"uid":71068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T11:06:03.000Z","msg":"有冇tg谷？"},{"pid":"77d0c6a85cdb2d76f3f725426b2a3fb54867e9de","tid":2241213,"uid":9178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T14:36:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"166442d45b7ab4c8c1dd9711d440666823336dfb","tid":2241213,"uid":9178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T23:57:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/asset